{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Gamepad API","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Gamepad_API","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Gamepad_API\">Gamepad API</a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Guias</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Gamepad_API/Using_the_Gamepad_API\">Using the Gamepad API</a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Games/Techniques/Controls_Gamepad_API\">Implementing controls using the Gamepad API</a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Interfaces</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Gamepad\"><code>Gamepad</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/GamepadButton\"><code>GamepadButton</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/GamepadEvent\"><code>GamepadEvent</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Navigator/getGamepads\"><code>Navigator.getGamepads()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eventos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window/gamepadconnected_event\"><code>Window</code>: <code>gamepadconnected</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window/gamepaddisconnected_event\"><code>Window</code>: <code>gamepaddisconnected</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>A <strong>Gamepad API&nbsp;</strong>é uma maneira dos desenvolvedores acessarem e responderem à sinais oriundos de gamepads e outros controladores de games de forma simples e consistente. A API contém três interfaces, dois eventos e uma função especialista, para responder aos gamepads sendo conectados e desconectados, e acessar outras informações sobre o próprio gamepad, e quais botões e outros controles estão sendo de fato passados.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"interfaces","title":"Interfaces","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"gamepad\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Gamepad\" title=\"The Gamepad interface of the Gamepad API defines an individual gamepad or other controller, allowing access to information such as button presses, axis positions, and id.\"><code>Gamepad</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Representa o gamepad/controlador conectado ao computador.</dd>\n <dt id=\"gamepadbutton\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GamepadButton\" title=\"The GamepadButton interface defines an individual button of a gamepad or other controller, allowing access to the current state of different types of buttons available on the control device.\"><code>GamepadButton</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Representa um botão num dos controles conectados.</dd>\n <dt id=\"gamepadevent\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GamepadEvent\" title=\"The GamepadEvent interface of the Gamepad API contains references to gamepads connected to the system, which is what the gamepad events Window.gamepadconnected and Window.gamepaddisconnected are fired in response to.\"><code>GamepadEvent</code></a></dt>\n <dd>O objeto de evento representando eventos disparados que são relacionados ao gamepad.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"experimental_gamepad_extensions","title":"Experimental Gamepad extensions","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"gamepadhapticactuator\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GamepadHapticActuator\" title=\"The GamepadHapticActuator interface of the Gamepad API represents hardware in the controller designed to provide haptic feedback to the user (if available), most commonly vibration hardware.\"><code>GamepadHapticActuator</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Representa o hardware no controlador designado à prover feedbacks táteis ao usuário (Se disponível), mais comumente um hardware de vibração.</dd>\n <dt id=\"gamepadpose\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GamepadPose\" title=\"The GamepadPose interface of the Gamepad API represents the pose of a WebVR controller at a given timestamp (which includes orientation, position, velocity, and acceleration information.)\"><code>GamepadPose</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Representa a \"localização\" de um controle (ex. posição e orientação no espaço 3D) no caso de um controlador WebVR.</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<p>Veja também as <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Gamepad#Experimental_extensions_to_Gamepad\">extensões para a interface de Gamepad</a>, para funcionalidades que permitem você acessar as informações acima.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"extensions_to_other_interfaces","title":"Extensions to other interfaces","isH3":true,"content":"<h4 id=\"navigator\">Navigator</h4>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"navigator.getgamepads_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Navigator/getGamepads\"><code>Navigator.getGamepads()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Uma extensão para o objeto <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a> que retorna um array&nbsp; de objetos <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Gamepad\"><code>Gamepad</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, um para cada controlador conectado.</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<h4 id=\"window_events\">Window events</h4>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"window.ongamepadconnected_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/gamepadconnected_event\"><code>Window.ongamepadconnected</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Representa um controlador de evento que irá rodar quando o gamepad é conectado (quando&nbsp;o&nbsp;evento <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/gamepadconnected_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">gamepadconnected (en-US)</a></code> for disparado).</dd>\n <dt id=\"window.ongamepaddisconnected_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/gamepaddisconnected_event\"><code>Window.ongamepaddisconnected</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Representa um controlador de evento que irá rodar quando o gamepad é desconectado (quando&nbsp;o&nbsp;evento <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/gamepaddisconnected_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">gamepaddisconnected (en-US)</a></code> for disparado).</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"guias_e_tutorias","title":"Guias e tutorias","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Gamepad_API/Using_the_Gamepad_API\">Using the Gamepad API</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Games/Techniques/Controls_Gamepad_API\">Implementing controls using the Gamepad API</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificações</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Estatus</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentários</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/gamepad/extensions.html\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"The 'Gamepad Extensions' specification\" rel=\" noopener\">Gamepad Extensions</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-ed\">Rascunho editorial</span></td>\n   <td>Defines the <a href=\"#experimental_gamepad_extensions\">Experimental Gamepad extensions</a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/gamepad/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Gamepad<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'The Gamepad API specification' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Rascunho atual</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.Gamepad","dataURL":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Gamepad_API/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://hacks.mozilla.org/2013/12/the-gamepad-api/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">The Gamepad API</a>&nbsp;por Ted Mielczarek and Robert Nyman</li>\n <li><a href=\"http://luser.github.io/gamepadtest/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Simple API demo page</a> (<a href=\"https://github.com/luser/gamepadtest\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">source</a>)</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Interfaces","id":"interfaces"},{"text":"Guias e tutorias","id":"guias_e_tutorias"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"A Gamepad API é uma maneira dos desenvolvedores acessarem e responderem à sinais oriundos de gamepads e outros controladores de games de forma simples e consistente. A API contém três interfaces, dois eventos e uma função especialista, para responder aos gamepads sendo conectados e desconectados, e acessar outras informações sobre o próprio gamepad, e quais botões e outros controles estão sendo de fato passados.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Gamepad API","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Gamepad API","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Gamepad API","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Gamepad API","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Gamepad API","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Gamepad API","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Gamepad API","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Gamepad API","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/gamepad_api","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/gamepad_api/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Gamepad_API","title":"Gamepad API"}],"pageTitle":"Gamepad API - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}